10\u20131212<br/>''with Maria'' || c. 1170<br/>son of [[Erard II of Brienne]] and Agnes de Montfaucon || [[Maria of Montferrat|Maria of Jerusalem]]<br/>14 September 1210<br/>one daughter<br/><br/>Stephanie of Armenia<br/>one son<br/><br/>[[Berengaria of Le\u00f3n]]<br/>1224<br/>4 children || 27 March 1237<br/>aged about 67\n|-\n|'''[[Isabella II of Jerusalem|Isabella II]]'''<br/>also called '''Yolande'''<br/>1212\u20131228<br/>''with Frederick from 1225'' ||  [[File:DeathofYolande-Isabella.jpg|100px]] || 1212<br/>daughter of [[John of Brienne]] and [[Maria of Montferrat|Queen Maria]] || [[Frederick II, Holy Roman Emperor]]<br/>9 November 1225<br/>2 children || 25 April 1228<br/>[[Andria, Italy|Andria]], [[Holy Roman Empire]]<br/>aged 16\n|-\n|'''[[Frederick II, Holy Roman Emperor|Frederick]]'''<br/>1225\u20131228<br/>''with Isabella II'' ||  [[File:Frederick II and eagle.jpg|100px]] || 1194<br/>son of [[Henry VI, Holy Roman Emperor]] and [[Constance, Queen of Sicily|Constance of Sicily]] || [[Constance of Aragon, Holy Roman Empress|Constance of Aragon]] <br/> 15 August 1209 <br/> one son <br/><br/> [[Isabella II of Jerusalem]]<br/>9 November 1225<br/>2 children<br/><br/>[[Isabella of England]] <br/> 15 July 1235<br/>4 children || 13 December 1250<br/>[[Apulia]], [[Holy Roman Empire]]<br/>aged 55\n|}\n\n===[[House of Hohenstaufen]] (1228\u20131268)===\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Monarch\n! Image\n! Birth\n! Marriages\n! Death\n|-\n|'''[[Conrad IV of Germany|Conrad II]]'''<br/>1228\u20131254 || [[File:Conrad IV of Germany.jpg|100px]] ||  25 April 1228<br/>[[Andria, Italy|Andria]], [[Holy Roman Empire]]<br/>son of [[Frederick II, Holy Roman Emperor]] and [[Isabella II of Jerusalem|Queen Isabella II]] || [[Elisabeth of Bavaria (1227\u20131273)|Elisabeth of Bavaria]]<br/>1 September 1246<br/>one son || 21 May 1254<br/>[[Lavello]], [[Holy Roman Empire]]<br/>aged 26\n|-\n|'''[[Conradin|Conrad III]]'''<br/>1254\u20131268 || [[File:Konradin.jpg|100px]] ||  25 March 1252<